{
  "stem": "9777.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans were asking for extremely amo-- big amounts of bribes for any kind of an action they could come with up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not to my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a youngster of 16 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe there wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you see, that-- the young people are very busy for themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Self-preservation, maybe you would call it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was nobody, really, who should be giving advice on the things, you know, that could organize.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a very good friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a cleaner for the Gestapo, one of the fancy hotels on the hill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The rich Jews, which were more, should we say, above the age who were took for forced labor or some physical inability, they did do a lot of torture, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wanted to know about monies and jewels and secrets and things which [INAUDIBLE] people have no access to, after my own knowledge.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were quite a few big manufacturers in Budapest of Jewish faith.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Which one had metal manufacturing and machinery manufacturing, they wanted to have information out of them, if they have any kind of connection to the Americans, the English or-- tremendous amount of torture was going on out there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really that I should say that I had seen anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever I heard from the young man, but he couldn't name no names.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Account of he cleaned up, excuse me, whatever that came out afterwards, you know, like, they tortured them, the blood or whatever else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was his job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't even know if--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was just telling me what he was doing the day before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we lived in the same building, so we didn't go out of our ways to meet or anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
